<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Aggredon</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-05-31 11:26:39</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Just laid the proverbial smack down on this Maugurim last night, and thought I'd share some info.<BR>
<BR>
~ Maugurim cons blue at lvl 30.<BR>
~ Maugurim was there waiting to be smacked down when I got to Kerra - I did not have to trigger her spawn.<BR>
~ The whore casts fear.<BR>
~ If you become afraid of Maugurim, and run away, the gorilla guards and assorted Kerra will smack Maugurim down.<BR>
~ Unfortunately if they smack down Maugurim you will get no icon.<BR>
~ After you have been KSd by the NPCs, go back and wait for Maugurim to respawn (still - needs no trigger). I don't have an exact time frame, but it wasn't ridiculously long. It took me 3x to finally resist the damn fear and kill her.<BR>
~ Stuns are great.<BR>
~ As soon as Maugurim spawns, she begins to buff herself.<BR>
~ I noticed no faction loss by smacking down Maugurim.<BR>
<BR>
As far as the rest of the quest goes, the ignot of the penitent is in the west water pillar in Upper Guk (loc is 206, neg 484 - per AllaKhazam). It wasn't that easy to see (for me) so just click on the bottom of the water pillar(near the middle).<BR>
<BR>
This particular quest requires only one bar of magnetized platinum.<BR>
<BR>
Hope you find some of the info useful!</font></td></tr></table>
